I also think we should standardize the special Supervertaler format for data export and reimport (back into Supervertaler). currently it is: Supervertaler bilingual table (DOcX)

However, I think we should offer this in two file formats: DOCX and TSV
 
and so we effectively merge:

- Supervertaler bilingual table (DOCX)
- Full data with metadata (TSV)

into a single identical logical/table format, but which the user can access and use in two file formats: docx/tsv

internally, it would be the same table, with all kids of useful data
just one inside a docx (for MS Word fans), the other in a tsv (for people who like csv editors)

we can tinker on tis format as we progress with the development of Supervertaler 
we could even i